{"tid":608060,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"車仔時期的馬達到底有幾屈機？","createTime":"2018-03-28T00:19:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T01:22:35.000Z","uid":63913,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"592e7106e48d5fc09d4eb7e82b27e2f7b7363013","tid":608060,"uid":63913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T00:19:30.000Z","msg":"一加盟就有貨交，連續兩年拎車仔最佳球員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果時打攻中勁到不得了，有罰球、助攻、埋門、過人同傳球。場場比賽都差不多出佢，打足幾十場都有表現。最可惜係摩佬覺得佢防守能力不足，先賣去魚拉特，點知最後連摩佬自己都過埋去。<br />\n<br />\n當年馬達絕對比得上今日的迪布尼，而家只淪為一個普通的翼位。<br />\n<br />\n附上當年車仔數據：<br />\n<br />\n11/12年度：出場：54；入球：12；助攻：20。<br />\n12/13年度：出場：64；入球：19；助攻：35。"},{"pid":"f920e866a2f80adfb47229f38ac9fec64c9184a3","tid":608060,"uid":53672,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T00:23:47.000Z","msg":"果年係車踢到風生水起賣佢果時真係r爆頭"},{"pid":"de911573fbc60c78a38be1bb5cfdad1f6f482743","tid":608060,"uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T00:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://image.wenweipo.com/2018/03/28/a28b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.wenweipo.com%2F2018%2F03%2F28%2Fa28b.jpg&h=bbd989a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5a019337f1980c6677824a43fd52e34ade09b6e","tid":608060,"uid":475,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T01:37:02.000Z","msg":"所以摩佬正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n迪布尼 馬達 沙拿 盧卡古<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5d92e72a393fc02e90b852ec6a9b2dcacab55e","tid":608060,"uid":19126,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:19:35.000Z","msg":"但覺得過到曼聯之後表現差左好多，一來唔適應，二來曼聯班人難夾。當年係車係勁，但都唔覺得勁過施華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今屆就係回緊塘"},{"pid":"3f398c51fd7af887a9495509625c4b9403bfe4a7","tid":608060,"uid":1166,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:34:53.000Z","msg":"49000 死全家"},{"pid":"a6f11fa600575657baad058bc0116871bed1f1c6","tid":608060,"uid":5649,"like":8,"dislike":10,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:40:15.000Z","msg":"迪布尼今季勁過佢成個車仔生涯好多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd45011856896dac7d801eadd1662f8129dbf05b","tid":608060,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:42:04.000Z","msg":"mkhitaryan &gt;kdb&gt;mata=silva&gt;cazorla"},{"pid":"30dd924dacb063a2d6a046ef59b868741b6813e9","tid":608060,"uid":63913,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:23:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>迪布尼今季勁過佢成個車仔生涯好多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跑動同身體質素就一定係迪布尼優勝，但馬達的進攻數據好突出。第二年直接參與53個入球，有邊個打到咁的數據？"},{"pid":"928c9067a2f9d31cfb441e24085fad01cc2fdc8f","tid":608060,"uid":68916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:23:40.000Z","msg":"召喚老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67148eeea9d6558a23aa994d541c5581e427dcd","tid":608060,"uid":4959,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"30dd924dacb063a2d6a046ef59b868741b6813e9","tid":608060,"uid":63913,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:23:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>迪布尼今季勁過佢成個車仔生涯好多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跑動同身體質素就一定係迪布尼優勝，但馬達的進攻數據好突出。第二年直接參與53個入球，有邊個打到咁的數據？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:27:09.000Z","msg":"C朗"},{"pid":"65fecfd474a727965daf5d6fd9f10dc3294a803d","tid":608060,"uid":54025,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:29:43.000Z","msg":"以波論波，比唔上依家kdb<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當年車條中場太soft，中場打獌依件廢物中場可以輕鬆贏(卡膠聰明)<br />\n<br />\n但對鏝條肉腸中場比人撞到組織唔到(迪莊，巴利，yaya)<br />\n<br />\n唔多唔少因為馬達一比人逼就收皮。<br />\n死左腳身型單薄無速度<br />\n<br />\n雖然同施華特點一樣，但施華既護波能力比佢強。<br />\n<br />\n再講，當年用佢做核心係聯賽真係無得爭。<br />\n歐聯佢係主力，但實際上當年贏一班老野咬緊牙關搏返黎，都唔係好關佢事。"},{"pid":"772c05d86a6c9cfdc38d6bc98b64c9c80a4420eb","tid":608060,"uid":54025,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:31:56.000Z","msg":"當年既佢係1線<br />\n<br />\n但依家kdb係講緊當今最強之一<br />\n<br />\n所以真心無得比。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實當年摩狗唔用佢我雖然有屌，但都覺得有道理<br />\n<br />\n最主要係屌佢完全唔比機會馬達試下同埋點解賣比獌聯<br />\n<br />\n我覺得如果當年遲半季先放馬達，英超隨時有機會贏到"},{"pid":"82be157003fca8022cc80413ce72788391b2dd85","tid":608060,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:43:02.000Z","msg":"買黎激活費托<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f148fbc452eac0b9be609e1569e9d5222a27b4d","tid":608060,"uid":78574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"65fecfd474a727965daf5d6fd9f10dc3294a803d","tid":608060,"uid":54025,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:29:43.000Z","msg":"以波論波，比唔上依家kdb<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當年車條中場太soft，中場打獌依件廢物中場可以輕鬆贏(卡膠聰明)<br />\n<br />\n但對鏝條肉腸中場比人撞到組織唔到(迪莊，巴利，yaya)<br />\n<br />\n唔多唔少因為馬達一比人逼就收皮。<br />\n死左腳身型單薄無速度<br />\n<br />\n雖然同施華特點一樣，但施華既護波能力比佢強。<br />\n<br />\n再講，當年用佢做核心係聯賽真係無得爭。<br />\n歐聯佢係主力，但實際上當年贏一班老野咬緊牙關搏返黎，都唔係好關佢事。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:45:20.000Z","msg":"屌你仆街成段都係我心聲<br />\n不過我都係好想馬達留隊<br />\n又好波又唔串又落力既球員都幾難得"},{"pid":"540c197c7891435fe2f4d456d9a73d3de5347892","tid":608060,"uid":61829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T05:00:18.000Z","msg":"用馬達打翼不如用馬隆達"},{"pid":"9d36e22d8486838f751dd64b515c8331943bbe96","tid":608060,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"540c197c7891435fe2f4d456d9a73d3de5347892","tid":608060,"uid":61829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T05:00:18.000Z","msg":"用馬達打翼不如用馬隆達"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T06:5